\id GLO - Mangga Buang NT [mmo] -Papua New Guinea 1981 (web 2014)
\h Vakasin Tatekin
\toc2 Vakasin Tatekin
\toc1 Vakasin Tatekin
\mt1 Vakasin Tatekin
\li1 \k Babilon\k* Hil ngeeyaata kand navu nambe Pita yuuh Jon lanêêl vakasin lak Babilon-anjo, ond manyinjo lanêêl vakasin lak Lom, in busin sen Pita yuuh Jon dandôô-to ond hil Lom dawiing va nipaya vaha vaha nambe sen hil Babilon dawiing-ambe lala mend ma bôôy-ato. Gangge 1 Pita 5:13*. Le hil vaalu kand navu nambe Jon hilin lak Babilon-ambe neep hôôk Taato Langaah 14:8-ato, ond hilin lak omaahonôôn pin sen nind baya in Kalisi be dayiis ngaamong vu yite hil-ato.
\li1 \k Betaani\k* Betaani ond me-bayêên timu le, Betaani yuuhapim. Ango neep ngaaho vu bel Yoladan, gangge Jon 1:28*, tonde ango neep ngaaho vu Yelusalem.
\li1 \k bik sipsip noow\k* Nambe sen Jon nêêl bik sipsip noow-ato ond hil Yuda lako Anutu-te vakasin vaalu lak bik sipsip vu munggin. Ti neep Eksodas 12, ond nêêl nambe hil layiis bik sipsip noow-ambe latêêy nihees ak bayêên, le mem Omaaho Bop-ate angela yi tombe me-yiis sil e, de la yiis hil Ijip amu. Gangge Hibluu-to 11:28*. Tonde ango neep Eksodas 29 ond nêêl nambe kul vaha sen datung salivangin-ato ond datung bik sipsip noow natu salivangin vu Anutu, ond datung samiin-ande soosin nalak busin pin. Tonde ti neep Jenesis 22:13* ond nêêl nambe Abalaam hatung sipsip ti tu salivangin vu Anutu lukalaah noow Isak ahembaan. Tonde ti neep Aisaia 53, ond nêêl nambe Omaaho Bop vu yate va nipaya lakala omaaho ti sen lohvu bik sipsip amelaas-ato be vaaku. Gangge Jon 1:29; 1 Pita 1:19; Taato Langaah 5:6*.
\li1 \k busin sawaasin\k* Hil Yuda davu sapa hôôk Anutu-te tanasin-ambe davu sawaah lohvu busin sen natu namaavaalu be vindak yuuh-ato pin, ond sil davu sawaah lak Salele pin. Tonde Yuda dako busin moos lak hôôk 6 kilok soosin-ambe nala hato soosin ango. Om sen ngaaho nalak in busin sawaasin, ond me-le lambiing kul hôôk 6 kilok soosin e, in soosin-anjo ond busin sawaasin. De yiiy ond yakangg navu sen Yesu kandi lak vu hil yimbin-atêêto nambe busin sawaasin, om yiiy naahe Sonda be yiiy navu sawaah hôôk Sonda. Gangge Matai 28:1*.
\li1 \k Esia\k* Taaku Esia sen haale lukaneep hôôk kaapiyaa-jo ond yoo taaku ti (provins), nganjo gêên ond hil dasupin taaku ti ti haalend-ambe danêêl haale bop nambe Asia. Gangge 2 Timoti 1:15*.
\li1 \k Genesaalet\k* Genesaalet ond yik taaku ti nando betum Galili nanyendangga, le danêêl bel-anju haale yaal, ti Genesaalet, ti Galili, de ti Taibilias. Gangge Luk 5:1*.
\li1 \k Glik\k* Hil Glik ond sil-ame Yuda le, de sil-ame hil Islel e, yik sil oo Glik, tonde silate taaku nando diin in Yuda-te taaku. Glik-ate taaku ond haale ango nambe Akaia. Tonde hil Glik ond sil ngeeyaata me-lawii-having Anutu le, yik sil ti ti lawii-having Anutu. Gangge Sinaale 16:1; 20:2*.
\li1 \k Helot\k* Yêêv Helot-anju ond omaaho yumbeyuuh haalend. Ti munggin ond danêêl nambe Helot Bop, ond yi sen yiis Islel noondin vu Betlehem-ambe layimb-ato, tode yimb taamusin. Gangge Matai 2:16-19*. Helot Bop noow ond danêêl haale nambe Helot Antipas, ond yii-jo sen katôôv Jon sen nalipis hil-ato ka. Tonde Helot Bop bu ond danêêl haale nambe Helot Aglipa I, ond sen yiis Jems-ambe yimb-ato, de hatung Pita lukala kalaambus, tonde Anutu wiing male ya be yimb. Gangge Sinaale 12*. Tonde ti ond Helot Bop kanu, tonde danêêl haale nambe Helot Aglipa 2, ond hako vanga Benaisi sen tangganaan ango-têêto tu vane, tonde vanga ango Dalusila sen lak vu yêêv bop Piliks sen yi Lom tii-to. Ond Aglipaa-ju sen yuuh vane lango Pol-ate vakasin neep Sisaliaa-to. Gangge Sinaale 25:13*.
\li1 \k hil sen dako taakis-ato\k* Hil Yuda dayi silate hil sen dako taakis-ato paya, in sil dako taakis vu sil, tombe davu silate mone nala vu gaaman vu Lom. Tonde lalak ni having nambe davu tatuhin sil-ande dahôôndak silate mone vaalu savok, de me-dako taakis nivalok e. Gangge Matai 18:17*.
\li1 \k Jon\k* Jon-anju ond hil namaavaalu haalend. Jon sen nalipis hil-ato ond Sakaalia noow, tonde Jon ango ond Pita mangganaan, gangge Jon 1:42; 21:15*. Tonde ti ond Sebedi noow Jon, tombe tu Yesu-te maanggêêm ti be kaavu banye nivasa, tonde kaavu 1 Jon, 2 Jon, 3 Jon, de kaavu Taato Langaah having. Tonde Jon ti ond hil Yuda-te yêêv ti, gangge Sinaale 4:6. Tonde Jon ti ond haale ango nambe Maak, ond yik Maak sen kaavu Yesu-te banye nivasaa-to, gangge Sinaale 12:25; 13:13; 15:37*.
\li1 \k Kalisi yuuh Mesia\k* Hil sen danêêl Anutu-te vakasin langaah-ato ond vaalu lanêêl vu hil Islel vu munggin nambe Anutu yoo holin omaaho ti vulôôt in nambe biing naam voon in dôôvu yiiy pin, ond danêêl hôôk sil lavand nambe kalisi, om Yuda pin datung mend in omaahôô-ju. Tombe sim taamusin Anutu wiing yite vakasin tii-jo nôôn ak hôôk sen wiing noow Yesu laam voon-ato, ondeey hil lanêêl yi nambe Kalisi, tombe lanêêl lôôt-ambe tu haale lak. Tonde haale Mesia hôôk Hiblu lavand, ond yik danggakook timu nambe sen haale Kalisi danggakook-anju. Gangge Jon 1:41*.
\li1 \k Omaahonôôn Noow\k* Yesu nêêl vakasin lak Omaahonôôn Noow ond yoo nêêl lak yi. In yi Anutu Noow, lemu laam voon-ambe tu omaahonôôn keen, tombe nanêêl vakasin nalak yi nambe Omaahonôôn Noow. Gangge Matai 9:6*. Tonde haale Omaahonôôn Noow-anjo ond yite vakasin oo neep munggin hôôk Danyel 7:13-14* nambe Daniel yi de Omaahonôôn Noow hato naale hôôk bayiimb alo tombe la vu omaaho sen nando metumin danggata osin danggataa-to, tonde vu niwêêk vu be tu omaaho lulemak, de hil pin lako haale lak, tombe hil taaku ti ti pin de nind naavi ti ti pin osin lavand ti ti pin ond le lavand hôôk yi timu haale, tombe yite niwêêk le nanjip danggata, tonde yoo le mongganggin hil danggata.
\li1 \k Palisai\k* Hil Yuda vaalu osin silate yêêv vaalu ond lalak Mose-te tanasin ani nivasa lôôt, le silate himbop-aso bôôy sil oo lanêêl tanasin vaalu having, tonde davu sapa yuuh ahondoos niwêêk lôôt nambe Mose-te tanasin pin-ato, ond danêêl sil nambe Palisai. Gangge Matai 15:1-2; 23:23; Sinaale 23:8*.
\li1 \k Pentikos\k* Haale Pentikos-anjo dangga nambe busin doo-yuuh-ambe nomaayuuh. Om Yuda-te busin bop busin haluusin nalung nala, tonde busin doo-yuuh-ambe nomaayuuh nala vêêl e mem dayi silate busin Pentikos, ond busin-anju sil datung salivangin vu Anutu in silate vanôôn nôôn ak. Gangge Sinaale 2:1; 20:16*.
\li1 \k Sadusi\k* Hil Yuda vaalu sen me-kand navu Anutu-te vakasin sen hil vaalu danêêl langaah-ato le, davu sapa Mose-te tanasin timu, de danêêl niwêêk lôôt nambe hil yimbin-ame le kandi jak e, ond danêêl sil nambe Sadusi, ond sil-ame ngeey e. Gangge Sinaale 23:8*.
\li1 \k Saion\k* Taku bop Yelusalem ond haale ango nambe Saion. Gangge Jon 12:15*.
\li1 \k Silvenes\k* Silvenes-anju ond haale ango nambe Silas, ond yik Silas sen yiiy naahe hôôk Sinaale-sote vakasin nambe nahôôvu Pol in kul lôôt-ato. Gangge Sinaale 18:5; 2 Kolint 1:19*.
\li1 \k Sisa\k* Hil Lom latu yêêv-ambe danggin hil Yuda, tombe hil Yuda daate taakis vu sil. Tonde hil Lom danêêl silate omaaho lulemak hôôk sil lavand nambe Sisa. Gangge Luk 2:1; Sinaale 25:10-12*.
\li1 \k wit\k* Wit-anju vanôoôn sen davu kaatuuh-ambe natu palawa lak le mem davu samu balet ak-ato. De hil daalôôh wit ond nalak nambe sen paandi be nayiis nôôn anipasiv nambe sen paandii-to. Gangge Luk 6:1-2; Sinaale 27:35,38*.
\li1 \k yis\k* Yis ond malaasin ti davu samu balet ak-ambe nalinj-ato. Tonde hil Yuda ond yik daya balet nambêênju nalak busin pin, lemu davu sapa hôôk silate gambum hôôk silate busin bop busin haluusin-ambe danêêlin yis. Gangge Matai 13:33; 26:17*. 
